title.narrative: OUTPUT 5.1 EVIDENCE GENERATION AND SYSTEM STRENGTHENING

description.narrative: Output 5.1 Government and selected partners staff have strengthened capacities on monitoring, analysing, generating and using evidence on socio-economic context to inform social protection and inclusion programming, which contributes to Access To Inclusive Social Protection, Access To Inclusive Social Protection (Covid), Reducing Child Poverty, Reducing Child Poverty (Covid). UNICEF aims to achieve this through Advocacy And Public Engagement, Developing And Leveraging Resources And Partnerships, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building, Systems Strengthening To Leave No One Behind. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: By 2022, more children in Yemen and their families who live in poverty (income and multi-dimensional) access adequate social protection and social services
